genova <gnva> signs definitive merger agreement
    davison, mich., march 25 - 
genova inc said it signed a definitive agreement for the previously
announced merger with <genova products inc>. under the agreement,
genova products will pay 5-3/8 dlrs a share for the 29 pct of genova's
outstanding common shares it does not already own. the company said it
plans to complete the transaction, which requires shareholder
approval, by the end of march. reuter 
